ed="T" n="0775c07"/><persName key="A004475">釋從諗</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000020642"><placeName>青州</placeName><placeName>臨淄</placeName></placeName>人也<ptr target="#n1562"/>。童稚之歲，孤介弗群，<lb
ed="T" n="0775c08"/>越二親之覊絆，超然離俗。乃投本州<placeName key="PL000000021092">龍興<lb
ed="T" n="0775c09"/>伽藍</placeName><ptr target="#n1563"/>，從師剪落。尋往<placeName key="PL000000023256"><placeName>嵩山</placeName><placeName>琉璃壇</placeName></placeName>納戒，<ref type="person" target="#A004475">師</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0775c10"/>勉之聽習，於經律但染指而已。聞<placeName key="PL000000016632">池陽</placeName><persName key="A003889">願<lb
ed="T" n="0775c11"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>道化翕如<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>，<persName key="A004475">諗</persName>執心定志，鑽仰忘疲。<persName key="A003889">南<lb
ed="T" n="0775c12"/>泉</persName>密付授<ref type="person" target="#A004475">之</ref>，滅跡匿端，坦然安樂。後於<placeName key="PL000000001058">趙<lb
ed="T" n="0775c13"/>郡</placeName>開物化迷，大行禪道。以<placeName key="PL000000000871">真定</placeName>帥<persName key="A010731">王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>阻<lb
ed="T" n="0775c14"/>兵，封疆多梗，朝廷患之。<persName key="A010731">王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>抗拒過制，而<lb
ed="T" n="0775c15"/>偏歸心於<persName key="A004475">諗</persName>。<persName key="A004475">諗</persName>嘗寄塵拂上<persName key="A010731">王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>曰：「<persName key="A010731">王</persName>若<lb
ed="T" n="0775c16"/>問何處得此拂子？答道<ref type="person" target="#A004475">老僧</ref>平生用不盡者<lb
ed="T" n="0775c17"/>物。」<ptr target="#n1564"/>凡所舉揚，天下傳之，號<persName key="A004475">趙州<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz15"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>去</sic><corr>法</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz15"/>道</persName><ptr target="#n400"/>。語錄<ptr target="#n1565"/><lb
ed="T" n="0775c18"/>大行，為世所貴也。</p>
